{{Top|leg}}
'''"The Lovers' Dilemma"''' was a famous [[Painting/Legends|piece of art]] created by the [[Artist/Legends|artist]] known as [[Walls]] who was a member of the [[Professiona Artists Guild]]. It was essentially a mixed media [[mood chamber]] and [[Holopainting/Legends|holographic painting]]. The piece was proudly displayed in the guild's permanent residence within the [[Perma (buildings)|Perma]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Elrood/Legends|Elrood]]. There were two similarly named events on the planet: [[The Lovers' Conflict]] and the [[The Lovers' Embrace]].

